124
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:32,700
¡Profesor Chang!

125
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:35,360
¡Profesor!

126
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,220
¿Eh?

127
00:13:36,220 --> 00:13:37,290
