128
00:13:37,580 --> 00:13:39,290
¡Mi querida alumna!

129
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:42,300
¡Cuánto tiempo sin vernos!

130
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,720
¡Profesor Chang!

131
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:48,640
